  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992460/extras/2855739e4b0c454819e61ec1c9d375c0.poster.avif?t=1760087780\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992460/extras/2855739e4b0c454819e61ec1c9d375c0.webm?t=1760087780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992460/extras/2855739e4b0c454819e61ec1c9d375c0.mp4?t=1760087780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SOUL PARK is a <strong>single-player  park builder game</strong> that immerses you in an afterlife ravaged by the Corruption, an entity that feeds on shadows and turns its hosts malevolent. <strong>Build a park at the gates of hell to bring back the light, and save the wandering souls.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Satanas is counting on you !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   Find tons of pop culture references and retro inspirations in a colorful universe imagined a passionate indie developer! <br><br>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Build</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build fancy rides </strong>and design your own roller coasters. Mix and match styles or optimize each space with <strong>6 permanent themes, along with seasonal ones!</strong> Decorate your park as you wish with <strong>over 90 objects</strong> with unique properties!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992460/extras/e3025c5fd325660a93cf59e3c6642747.poster.avif?t=1760087780\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992460/extras/e3025c5fd325660a93cf59e3c6642747.webm?t=1760087780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992460/extras/e3025c5fd325660a93cf59e3c6642747.mp4?t=1760087780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <u>Repair</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The rides are breaking down! Fix them by playing unique mini-games</strong> or hire employees to do the dirty work for you! Each theme comes with its own mini-game, ranging from puzzles, to rhythm games, to archaeology.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992460/extras/0b0f0a3bd2eb7214e907139e11959bc1.poster.avif?t=1760087780\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992460/extras/0b0f0a3bd2eb7214e907139e11959bc1.webm?t=1760087780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992460/extras/0b0f0a3bd2eb7214e907139e11959bc1.mp4?t=1760087780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Progress</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb the ladder, <strong>unlock new products</strong> in the progress tree, and earn dozens of cosmetics as a reward for your progress!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992460/extras/b2cedce26cd12a2c448d21241b755b5c.poster.avif?t=1760087780\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992460/extras/b2cedce26cd12a2c448d21241b755b5c.webm?t=1760087780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992460/extras/b2cedce26cd12a2c448d21241b755b5c.mp4?t=1760087780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Choose</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Judge the souls' mini-sins</strong> and decide who is worthy to enter your park! Discover the behaviors of different types of customers and watch the effects they have on your park.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992460/extras/bc2f66711f1792288bea0c5fb116b3cf.poster.avif?t=1760087780\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992460/extras/bc2f66711f1792288bea0c5fb116b3cf.webm?t=1760087780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992460/extras/bc2f66711f1792288bea0c5fb116b3cf.mp4?t=1760087780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992460/extras/707133e87c3ea82892fedc64a6896478.poster.avif?t=1760087780\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992460/extras/707133e87c3ea82892fedc64a6896478.webm?t=1760087780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992460/extras/707133e87c3ea82892fedc64a6896478.mp4?t=1760087780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In SOUL PARK, <strong>take on challenges in campaign mode</strong> and win exclusive rewards, or <strong>let your imagination run wild with the creative mode</strong>! Peculiar encounters await you on the path to redemption...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992460/extras/9425af41ce176d92898ef829fe44c692.poster.avif?t=1760087780\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992460/extras/9425af41ce176d92898ef829fe44c692.webm?t=1760087780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992460/extras/9425af41ce176d92898ef829fe44c692.mp4?t=1760087780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
